Option Strict On\nOption Infer On\n\nModule Module1\n    Sub Main()\n        Dim numbers = {1, 2, 3, 4, 5}\n\n        ' Using LINQ to select even numbers with anonymous type\n        Dim evenNumbers = From number In numbers\n                          Where number Mod 2 = 0\n                          Select New With {.Number = number}\n\n        For Each evenNumber In evenNumbers\n            Console.WriteLine("Even Number: " & evenNumber.Number)\n        Next\n    End Sub\nEnd Module